creator: QED
descriptionHtml:
ScanSpectrum is a series of portable spectrometers enabling users to bring the lab to the field.

Soils, waters, plants, and other specimens requiring dry and wet chemistry analyses can be now be executed in the field with high precision. Built in-house by QED (https://qed.ai), our technologies replicate the performance of laboratory equipment, at a small fraction of the price. NIR spectroscopy and colorimetry are brought into the palm of your hand by interfacing ScanSpectrum hardware with your Android smartphone.

** Note that you must have QED hardware to use this software!! Your phone cannot become a spectrometer using an Android app alone, it's impossible! Please visit https://url.qed.ai/scanspectrum-request if you are interested in partnership. **
descriptionShort: Bring the lab to the field with ScanSpectrum.
